headline: CDW Corporation (CDW) Hurt Wedgewood Partners’ Performance in Q4 and 2024
summary: Wedgewood Partners, an investment management company, released its fourth-quarter 2024 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. In the fourth quarter, Wedgewood Composite’s net return was 5.5% compared to the Standard & Poor’s 2.4%, the Russell 1000 Growth Index’s 7.1%, and the Russell 1000 Value Index’s -2.0% return for the same period.
